title: Gov't Mule - 2013-01-19 Negril, Jamaica [FLAC]
description:
Since 2010 Gov't mule play at the 'Island Exodus' festival  in Negril, Jamaica. That's the online release of the performance from January 19, 2013. Notable is the reggae-version of 'The Joker'.
